    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What happens when a video game character is self-aware?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cadulium follows the stories of Maia and Maria.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maia is a video game character who is followed everywhere she goes, and she doesn’t know why. She fights for survival while trying to solve her mystery and understand her reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762250/extras/aae9455d8d46c63b3235b06fe0d4ef36.avif?t=1769569720\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maria is a cryptic character. She &quot;works at the University.&quot; She blogs (and is on social media) under the username of IamNamedMaria, where she speculates about the nature of reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762250/extras/22bafa8169acdf771e30aba8cbdf12cc.avif?t=1769569720\" width=710 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: Screenshots are 3D, not photos.</p>",
